column10: EmissionFactorDataSource

Based on IEA data from the IEA (2021) Emissions Factors,  http://wds.iea.org/wds/pdf/WorldCO2_documentation.pdf. All rights reserved; as modified by Salesforce. 

NOTE: IEA gives emissions factor data for CO2, CH4 and N2O. Values for CH4 and N2O are given by IEA in converted CO2e units, where IEA has applied global warming potentials (GWP) from the 4th Assessment of the IPCC. Salesforce has modified this data to show unconverted CH4 and N2O values in the Location-Based Emissions Factors page section. Salesforce's value for Total CO2e uses GWP values from IPCC AR5.

Values for CH4 and N2O are given by IEA in converted CO2e units, where IEA has applied global warming potentials (GWP) from the 4th Assessment of the IPCC. Salesforce has modified this data to show unconverted CH4 and N2O values in the Location-Based Emissions Factors page section. Salesforce's value for Total CO2e uses GWP values from IPCC AR5.
